WEBVTT

00:00:00.746 --> 00:00:03.452
Bolaligimda doim superqahramon 
bo’lishni istardim.

00:00:03.476 --> 00:00:06.912
Dunyoni qutqarish va hammani 
baxtli qilishni xohlardim.

00:00:06.936 --> 00:00:10.729
Ammo orzularim ro’yobi uchun 
g’ayritabiiy kuch kerakligini bilardim.

00:00:10.753 --> 00:00:12.976
Kripton sayyorasidan 
intergalaktik obyektlarni

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:16.489
topish uchun tasavvurimdagi 
sayohatlarga chiqardim,

00:00:16.513 --> 00:00:19.227
bu o’ta maroqli edi, ammo 
undan aytarli natija chiqmasdi.

00:00:20.061 --> 00:00:21.800
Voyaga yetib ilmiy-fantastika

00:00:21.824 --> 00:00:24.976
g’ayritabiiy kuchlarning yaxshi 
manbai emasligini anglaganimda,

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:28.322
foydaliroq haqiqatni izlab topish 
uchun haqiqiy

00:00:28.346 --> 00:00:29.976
ilm-fan sayohatiga otlandim.